{"tid":1966174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邊爐家族康復者：家族集體感染付出沉重代價","createTime":"2020-04-10T04:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T06:35:16.000Z","uid":34551,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4201a2348aa1f2daefe709fcca404bc6e93a166e","tid":1966174,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】本港新冠病毒疫情爆發以來出現多個感染群組，其中最早的「邊爐家族」群組，有康復者表示，後悔當時自己與家人陸續有病徵後，仍然招待親戚到家中拜年，提醒市民要保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的Calvin是「邊爐群組」感染者之一，連他在內家族共十一人，在大年初二打邊爐後染病。親戚的兩名同事亦確診，而Calvin是最早確診的一個。<br />\n<br />\nCalvin留醫八日出院，沒有明顯後遺症，是群組中最早出院的，亦是香港第二名新型冠狀病毒康復患者。家人已陸續康復，只有91歲婆婆，因自身疾病仍在普通病房。<br />\n<br />\n他表示很後悔大家掉以輕心，一家人付出沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\nCalvin出院後與親友關係更親密，多了打電話互通近況，現實中的社交距離則一直維持。他表示，會珍惜家人和朋友的感情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387356&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi66f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=13da7e44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387356&h=9532054c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=387356</a>"},{"pid":"40821a8714aafe9c7c6671b089c9e7b83f44a14a","tid":1966174,"uid":63779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"人地成家都無事，個狗長咁渣既。"},{"pid":"4b695e1a36328aa07844e8bf75c173765cfd4c2b","tid":1966174,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<br />\n文宣要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［網軍召集］海外手足fb比五毛洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1966095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1966095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3faa3c9f4aa5e3f6bb52a6a45fa3d3124d92df5","tid":1966174,"uid":268519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04: